do you mean?" his words cool and direct. It is possible that he really
didn't know what Hydras was talking about, but then again he could be
just testing him in some way.

The stassis pods where the protoforms were housed both showed that
they were in perfect health, all lights were green. Cables ran from
them to various computers, each of them humming quietly with power as
glowing tendrils of energy flowled along thir length.
